Version: 0.6.2
Date: 2025-09-25

Current Task: Plan Annual Cost Analysis Report
Phase: 1 (Planning)

Goal: Finalize the data-gathering logic and UI/UX for the "Annual Cost Analysis" report, including summary metrics, a detailed breakdown table, and a flexible, multi-view chart for trend analysis.

Key Objectives (this phase):

Confirm the calculation logic for Blood, Antibody, and Other Raw Materials costs for a given year.

Define the structure and columns for the detailed cost breakdown table.

Solidify the requirements for the flexible (Annual/Quarterly/Monthly) spend chart.

